<br>
After extensive study into ALL of them and ALL of the combat styles and skills all I can say is I am OVERWHELMED at the depth of each class and style.<br>
<br>
Trying to play more than one class and differing style on more than one server would be exceedingly dificult. The fighting styles have combos and strings of attacks best performed one after the other and in a certain situation or sequence of events!<br>
<br>
I was honestly flabbergasted at the depth of these styles and just how different they were!<br>
<br>
Having said that I believe I have further reduced my choices and am now confident I know what I want to play where.<br>
<br>
Albion <br>
Mercenary either highlander or sarcen.<br>
Infiltrator Sarcen<br>
I toyed with the armsman idea and tho not completely ruling it out it is unlikely.<br>
<br>
Hiberian<br>
Blademaster Firbolg<br>
Champion Celt<br>
<br>
Midgard<br>
Thane Norseman<br>
Berserker Troll<br>
<br>
I do know I will play melee based and not a pure caster, at least for now.<br>
<br>
I'd recomend anyone considering a melee type to go to :<br>
<br>
copland.udel.edu/~trevor/...ndex.shtml<br>
<br>
And then to the Skills and Styles section and look over the amount of info there. I really believe a melee class in DAoC is going to be MUCH MUCH more challenging than any other MMORPG ever created to date.<br>
<br>
I am excited! <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub15.ezboard.com/fdaggersincamelotfrm1.showMessage?topicID=15.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub15.ezboard.com/fdaggersincamelotfrm1.showMessage?topicID=22.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub15.ezboard.com/fdaggersincamelotfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23.topic><img src=http://dancingdruid.homestead.com/files/add.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub15.ezboard.com/fdaggersincamelotfrm1.threadControl?topicID=23.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub15.ezboard.com/fdaggersincamelotfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=23.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub15.ezboard.com/fdaggersincamelotfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=23.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub15.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="daggersincamelotfrm24">General<option value="daggersincamelotfrm1">DAoC General<option value="daggersincamelotfrm23">Announcements<option value="daggersincamelotfrm2">Events<option value="daggersincamelotfrm4">Trade Skills<option value="daggersincamelotfrm3">In Game Quests<option value="daggersincamelotfrm5">Treasury<option value="daggersincamelotfrm17">Game Mechanic Discussions<option value="daggersincamelotfrm26">Looking For Group<option value="daggersincamelotfrm6">